      </debateSection>
      <debateSection>
        <heading>INTRODUCTION OF BILLS</heading>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MR. SPEAKER : Before we do Notices of Motion this morning, I'd like to have a little personal note here this morning. Our Page Scott Nordlund will be leaving us tomorrow, as he is going over to Europe to play professional football. Scott will be joining the Elmshorn Fighting Pirates in Germany for a six-month contract, with calls from the Blue Bombers, the Rough Riders, and the Lions. We wish you all the best, Scott, in your future endeavours. (Applause)</p>
        </speech>
