        <speech by="#9498b4ab-a8b9-42d9-8425-0c8d270f1612">
          <from>MR. LLOYD HINES</from>
          <p>MR. LLOYD HINES : Mr. Speaker, I would like to direct the Assembly's attention to the east gallery and introduce Councillor Fin Armsworthy who is with the Municipality of the District of Guysborough, formerly with the Town of Canso where he served for 14 years. I must say he has made a seamless transition onto the new council and has served the municipality as well as he had done for his former municipality. I would ask the Assembly to welcome him here today. (Applause)</p>
